b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":582,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Augments, a New Game Element, Are Coming Soon!","message":"<div>Hello, adventurers!<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>The new augments game element will be added <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1563170400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div>\\u30fbAugments will be unlocked when you clear chapter 9 of the main campaign, which will also be added <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1563170400\\"><\/span>.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Use augments on adventurers, weapons, dragons, and wyrmprints to upgrade them further.<\/div><div>See below for info on augments and more.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><u>1. Clear chapter 9 of the main campaign!<\/u><\/div><div>Clearing chapter 9 of the main campaign will unlock the new augments feature.<\/div><div>Additionally, you can get some of the special items required for augmentation as clear rewards.<\/div><div>The special items you acquire can be used on the Upgrade screen.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><u>2. Use special items on the Upgrade screen to power up!<\/u><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/873863d72c714b823c098e5aed4180df.png\\"><\/div><div>You can use some of the special items to increase strength and others to increase HP, both up to a maximum of +50.<\/div><div>You will be able to obtain these special items in Astral Raids, which will are coming soon.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><u>3. Collect Astral Pieces!<\/u><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f7c05b13ffbdef2c47a0d9b3be241d9c.png\\"><\/div><div>After <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1562824800\\"><\/span>, Astral Pieces can be obtained by clearing main campaign quests and event quests.<\/div><div>\\u30fbYou will not receive astral pieces for clearing quests while Astral Raids are active.<\/div><div>\\u30fbThe maximum number of Astral Pieces you can hold is 300.<\/div><div>\\u30fbIf you obtain Astral Pieces after reaching the limit, those Astral Pieces will be lost.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><u>4. Challenge Astral Raids!<\/u><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/02a67e7a6f182777abdf3f7ddfb853ae.png\\"><\/div><div>Astral Raids are event quests where you can fight against past raid bosses for a limited time.<\/div><div>To challenge Astral Raids quests, you will need to use Astral Pieces.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div><u>5. Clear Astral Raids to get rewards!<\/u><\/div><div><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f08c5af7d0e38bb4be9a95e3b7411156.png\\"><\/div><div>In addition to the special items used in augmentation, when you clear Astral Raids you can get Astral Shards.<\/div><div>Astral Shards can be traded in the Treasure Trade for the special items used in augmentation.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1562824800,"prev_article_id":"567","next_article_id":"544","image_path":"","update_time":1562823046}}}'